WEBVTT

00:03:28.760 --> 00:03:30.216
The Dogon,

00:03:30.240 --> 00:03:32.096
another great culture in Mali,

00:03:32.120 --> 00:03:33.776
called it "po,"

00:03:33.800 --> 00:03:35.440
or, "the seed of the universe."

00:03:36.480 --> 00:03:38.816
In that ancient culture's mythology,

00:03:38.840 --> 00:03:42.600
the entire universe
sprouted from a seed of fonio.

00:03:44.440 --> 00:03:47.456
Aside from its purported
mystical properties,

00:03:47.480 --> 00:03:50.000
fonio is a miracle grain in many aspects.

00:03:51.520 --> 00:03:53.056
It is nutritious,

00:03:53.080 --> 00:03:56.856
particularly rich
in methionine and cysteine,

00:03:56.880 --> 00:04:01.256
two amino acids that are deficient
